{"tid":1420031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【疊被新境界】【李漢民.jpg】 深圳公安演練　逾千警力防暴槍驅散穿黑衣戴頭盔示威者  熊大大嚇鬼？？？ 過黎打爛金蛋囉","createTime":"2019-08-06T03:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:19:54.000Z","uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8220a6ce93e99acc44019cc7e2e23b444572fe47","tid":1420031,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472999-20190806.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472999-20190806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=55039a30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472999-20190806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fd97c15a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472999-20190806.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n2019-08-06 HKT 11:15<br />\n<br />\n深圳市公安局早上10時半，在寶安區海濱廣場舉行夏季練兵，模擬特警演練和應急處置突發事件。<br />\n<br />\n行動名為「深圳亮劍」， 模擬出動1500人警力，面對2000名示威者的場面。深圳市公安局在官方微博直播，大批特警人員一字排開，手持長盾牌組成多個分隊，應對身穿黑色衣服、戴上頭盔、口罩，以及手持標語的示威者，現場廣播起初形容他們為滋事分子。<br />\n<br />\n示威者隨後衝擊不斷升級，他們高叫口號，用磚頭、木棒、鐵馬和火燒手推車，衝擊特警的防線，又掟「汽油彈」，現場廣播改為形容示威者是暴徒。特警其後向天施放催淚煙和防暴槍，驅散示威者， 並拘捕部分人，成功處置暴力騷亂事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QdpXQwT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQdpXQwT.jpg&h=d4bf2d38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MPYaq5g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMPYaq5g.jpg&h=3dfcefff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L1dNtiD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL1dNtiD.jpg&h=e9c25d3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f262f19d150d74e4bbe71dfad41674e8bfae9bac","tid":1420031,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03